  "abstract": "Chickpea (Cicer ariethtim L) is a mandate crop of International Crops Research Institute for the Semi-Arid Tropics (ICRISAT). The crop has fewer pest problems khan other legumes, Heliothis arimgtra is the major past in most chickpea growing areas and is polyphagous attacking many crop species.",
